‚ö†Ô∏è Important Disclaimer
All payments are estimates only and are subject to further price and yield changes. The information provided in this calculator is for informational purposes only. Actual payments may vary based on individual circumstances, final USDA determinations, acreage reporting, and other factors. Elite Ag Insurance makes no warranties or guarantees regarding the accuracy of this information and cannot be held liable for any decisions made based on these estimates.
[1] PLC Payment Calculations: PLC (Price Loss Coverage) payments are based on PLC Yields as established at the Farm Service Agency (FSA). The payments shown in this calculator are based on 75% of the Expected County Yields. Individual farm yields may differ.
[2] ECO Payment Calculations: ECO (Enhanced Coverage Option) payments are based on 100% of the Expected County Yield as determined by the Risk Management Agency (RMA). Each farmer's actual payment may be slightly higher or lower depending on their individual Actual Production History (APH) relative to the Expected County Yield. Your specific APH and coverage level will affect final indemnity calculations.
[3] Data Sources: Payment estimates are calculated using FSA program parameters, RMA county yields, and current commodity prices. All data is subject to official USDA updates and final determinations.
